<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Imperio de Automatización — Alexis</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Bebas+Neue&family=DM+Mono:wght@400;500&family=Barlow:wght@300;400;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
:root{
  --bg:#080810;--s1:#0f0f1a;--s2:#141422;--card:#181828;
  --b1:#1e1e32;--b2:#2a2a45;--b3:#3a3a60;
  --cyan:#00e5ff;--cyan2:rgba(0,229,255,.1);--cyan3:rgba(0,229,255,.05);
  --grn:#00ff87;--grn2:rgba(0,255,135,.1);
  --amb:#ffb300;--amb2:rgba(255,179,0,.1);
  --red:#ff4757;--red2:rgba(255,71,87,.1);
  --blu:#4488ff;--blu2:rgba(68,136,255,.1);
  --pur:#b06aff;--pur2:rgba(176,106,255,.1);
  --txt:#dde0f0;--dim:#7070a0;--faint:#3a3a60;
}
*{margin:0;padding:0;box-sizing:border-box}
html{scroll-behavior:smooth}
body{background:var(--bg);color:var(--txt);font-family:'Barlow',sans-serif;overflow-x:hidden;min-height:100vh}

.bg-orbs{position:fixed;inset:0;pointer-events:none;z-index:0;overflow:hidden}
.orb{position:absolute;border-radius:50%;filter:blur(100px);will-change:transform;animation:drift 25s ease-in-out infinite alternate}
.orb1{width:500px;height:500px;top:-150px;left:-150px;background:radial-gradient(circle,rgba(0,229,255,.05),transparent 70%)}
.orb2{width:400px;height:400px;bottom:-100px;right:-100px;background:radial-gradient(circle,rgba(176,106,255,.04),transparent 70%);animation-delay:-12s}
.orb3{width:300px;height:300px;top:40%;left:40%;background:radial-gradient(circle,rgba(0,255,135,.03),transparent 70%);animation-delay:-6s}
@keyframes drift{0%{transform:translate(0,0)}100%{transform:translate(25px,15px)}}

.bg-grid{position:fixed;inset:0;pointer-events:none;z-index:0;
  background-image:linear-gradient(var(--b1) 1px,transparent 1px),linear-gradient(90deg,var(--b1) 1px,transparent 1px);
  background-size:40px 40px;opacity:.35}

.wrap{max-width:1300px;margin:0 auto;padding:0 20px 80px;position:relative;z-index:1}

header{padding:40px 0 28px;display:flex;align-items:flex-end;justify-content:space-between;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:16px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--b1);margin-bottom:32px}
.logo{font-family:'Bebas Neue',sans-serif;font-size:3rem;letter-spacing:8px;line-height:1;
  background:linear-gradient(120deg,var(--cyan),var(--grn) 55%,var(--amb));
  -webkit-background-clip:text;-webkit-text-fill-color:transparent;background-clip:text;
  filter:drop-shadow(0 0 20px rgba(0,229,255,.25))}
.tagline{font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:10px;color:var(--dim);letter-spacing:2px;margin-top:4px;text-transform:uppercase}
.hpills{display:flex;gap:8px;flex-wrap:wrap}
.hp{font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:10px;padding:5px 12px;border-radius:4px;letter-spacing:1px;border:1px solid}
.hp.c{border-color:rgba(0,229,255,.3);color:var(--cyan);background:var(--cyan2)}
.hp.g{border-color:rgba(0,255,135,.3);color:var(--grn);background:var(--grn2)}
.hp.a{border-color:rgba(255,179,0,.3);color:var(--amb);background:var(--amb2)}

.tabs{display:flex;gap:6px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:32px;position:sticky;top:0;z-index:50;
  padding:12px 0;background:linear-gradient(var(--bg) 85%,transparent)}
.tab{font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:11px;padding:8px 16px;border-radius:5px;
  border:1px solid var(--b2);background:var(--s1);color:var(--dim);cursor:pointer;
  letter-spacing:1px;transition:all .18s;white-space:nowrap}
.tab:hover{color:var(--txt);border-color:var(--b3)}
.tab.active{background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(0,229,255,.12),rgba(0,255,135,.06));border-color:var(--cyan);color:var(--cyan)}

.sec{display:none;animation:fadeIn .3s ease}
.sec.active{display:block}
@keyframes fadeIn{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(8px)}to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0)}}

.intro{background:linear-gradient(135deg,rgba(0,229,255,.05),rgba(176,106,255,.03));
  border:1px solid rgba(0,229,255,.12);border-radius:12px;padding:20px 24px;
  margin-bottom:32px;font-size:.88rem;line-height:1.8;color:var(--dim)}
.intro strong{color:var(--cyan)}

.cat{margin-bottom:36px}
.cat-head{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:14px;margin-bottom:18px;padding-bottom:12px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--b1)}
.cat-icon{width:38px;height:38px;border-radius:9px;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:17px;flex-shrink:0}
.cat-title{font-family:'Bebas Neue',sans-serif;font-size:1.25rem;letter-spacing:4px}
.cat-badge{margin-left:auto;font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:9px;color:var(--dim);padding:2px 8px;border:1px solid var(--b2);border-radius:3px}

.grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(275px,1fr));gap:13px}
.grid2{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(330px,1fr));gap:13px}

.card{background:var(--card);border:1px solid var(--b1);border-radius:11px;padding:17px;
  transition:transform .18s,border-color .18s,box-shadow .18s;position:relative;overflow:hidden}
.card::before{content:'';position:absolute;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:2px;opacity:0;transition:opacity .2s}
.card:hover{transform:translateY(-2px);border-color:var(--b3);box-shadow:0 6px 24px rgba(0,0,0,.35)}
.card:hover::before{opacity:1}
.card.cc::before{background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--cyan),var(--grn))}
.card.cg::before{background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--grn),var(--amb))}
.card.ca::before{background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--amb),var(--red))}
.card.cr::before{background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--red),var(--pur))}
.card.cp::before{background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--pur),var(--cyan))}
.card.cb::before{background:linear-gradient(90deg,var(--blu),var(--cyan))}

.card-top{display:flex;gap:11px;align-items:flex-start;margin-bottom:9px}
.card-em{font-size:21px;line-height:1;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:2px}
.card-name{font-size:.9rem;font-weight:700;line-height:1.3;margin-bottom:3px}
.card-tool{font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:1.5px;text-transform:uppercase}
.cc .card-tool{color:var(--cyan)}.cg .card-tool{color:var(--grn)}.ca .card-tool{color:var(--amb)}
.cr .card-tool{color:var(--red)}.cp .card-tool{color:var(--pur)}.cb .card-tool{color:var(--blu)}
.card-desc{font-size:.78rem;color:var(--dim);line-height:1.65}
.card-tags{display:flex;gap:5px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:9px}
.tag{font-size:9px;padding:2px 7px;border-radius:3px;font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;letter-spacing:.5px;border:1px solid}
.tf{border-color:rgba(0,255,135,.25);color:var(--grn);background:var(--grn2)}
.tc{border-color:rgba(0,229,255,.25);color:var(--cyan);background:var(--cyan2)}
.ta{border-color:rgba(255,179,0,.25);color:var(--amb);background:var(--amb2)}
.tm{border-color:rgba(68,136,255,.25);color:var(--blu);background:var(--blu2)}
.tp{border-color:rgba(176,106,255,.25);color:var(--pur);background:var(--pur2)}
.tai{border-color:rgba(255,71,87,.25);color:var(--red);background:var(--red2)}

/* WEEK */
.week-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(7,1fr);gap:8px;margin-bottom:20px}
@media(max-width:900px){.week-grid{grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr)}}
@media(max-width:500px){.week-grid{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr)}}
.day-card{background:var(--s2);border:1px solid var(--b1);border-radius:9px;padding:12px;cursor:pointer;transition:all .18s;position:relative}
.day-card:hover,.day-card.open{border-color:var(--cyan);background:rgba(0,229,255,.04)}
.day-card.open .day-arrow{transform:rotate(90deg)}
.day-name{font-family:'Bebas Neue',sans-serif;font-size:.95rem;letter-spacing:3px;margin-bottom:3px}
.day-preview{font-size:9px;color:var(--dim);line-height:1.5}
.day-count{display:inline-block;margin-top:6px;font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:9px;padding:2px 6px;border-radius:3px}
.day-arrow{position:absolute;top:11px;right:11px;font-size:9px;color:var(--dim);transition:transform .2s}
.day-expanded{display:none;background:var(--s1);border:1px solid var(--b2);border-radius:11px;padding:22px;margin-bottom:16px;animation:fadeIn .22s ease}
.day-expanded.show{display:block}
.day-exp-title{font-family:'Bebas Neue',sans-serif;font-size:1.6rem;letter-spacing:5px;margin-bottom:18px}
.task-block{margin-bottom:18px}
.block-title{font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:9px;letter-spacing:2px;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--amb);margin-bottom:9px;padding-bottom:6px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--b1)}
.task-item{display:flex;gap:10px;align-items:flex-start;padding:9px 11px;border-radius:7px;margin-bottom:6px;background:var(--card);border:1px solid var(--b1);transition:border-color .15s}
.task-item:hover{border-color:var(--b3)}
.tdot{width:7px;height:7px;border-radius:50%;flex-shrink:0;margin-top:5px}
.dc{background:var(--cyan)}.dg{background:var(--grn)}.da{background:var(--amb)}.dp{background:var(--pur)}.dr{background:var(--red)}.db{background:var(--blu)}
.task-txt{font-size:.8rem;line-height:1.5;color:var(--txt)}
.task-sub{font-size:.7rem;color:var(--dim);margin-top:2px}

/* ROADMAP */
.roadmap{display:flex;flex-direction:column}
.rm-step{display:flex;gap:20px;padding-bottom:26px}
.rm-step:last-child{padding-bottom:0}
.rm-left{display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;width:44px;flex-shrink:0}
.rm-dot{width:44px;height:44px;border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-size:17px;border:2px solid;flex-shrink:0;z-index:1}
.rm-line{width:2px;flex:1;margin-top:6px;min-height:28px}
.rm-step:nth-child(1) .rm-dot{border-color:var(--cyan);background:var(--cyan2)} .rm-step:nth-child(1) .rm-line{background:linear-gradient(var(--cyan),var(--grn))}
.rm-step:nth-child(2) .rm-dot{border-color:var(--grn);background:var(--grn2)} .rm-step:nth-child(2) .rm-line{background:linear-gradient(var(--grn),var(--amb))}
.rm-step:nth-child(3) .rm-dot{border-color:var(--amb);background:var(--amb2)} .rm-step:nth-child(3) .rm-line{background:linear-gradient(var(--amb),var(--pur))}
.rm-step:nth-child(4) .rm-dot{border-color:var(--pur);background:var(--pur2)} .rm-step:nth-child(4) .rm-line{background:linear-gradient(var(--pur),var(--red))}
.rm-step:nth-child(5) .rm-dot{border-color:var(--red);background:var(--red2)} .rm-step:nth-child(5) .rm-line{background:linear-gradient(var(--red),var(--blu))}
.rm-step:nth-child(6) .rm-dot{border-color:var(--blu);background:var(--blu2)}
.rm-content{flex:1;padding-top:8px}
.rm-title{font-size:.98rem;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:5px}
.rm-desc{font-size:.8rem;color:var(--dim);line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:9px}
.rm-tools{display:flex;gap:6px;flex-wrap:wrap}
.rmt{font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:10px;padding:3px 9px;border-radius:4px;background:var(--s2);border:1px solid var(--b2);color:var(--txt)}

/* STACK */
.sg{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(195px,1fr));gap:10px}
.sc{background:var(--card);border:1px solid var(--b1);border-radius:9px;padding:15px;transition:all .18s}
.sc:hover{border-color:var(--b3);transform:translateY(-1px)}
.sc-em{font-size:24px;margin-bottom:9px}
.sc-label{font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:9px;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:2px;color:var(--dim);margin-bottom:4px}
.sc-app{font-weight:700;font-size:.9rem;margin-bottom:3px}
.sc-desc{font-size:.73rem;color:var(--dim);line-height:1.5}
.sc-free{display:inline-block;font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:9px;margin-top:7px;padding:2px 6px;border-radius:3px;background:var(--grn2);border:1px solid rgba(0,255,135,.2);color:var(--grn)}

/* ASSISTANTS */
.ag{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(330px,1fr));gap:13px}
.ac{background:var(--card);border:1px solid var(--b1);border-radius:11px;padding:19px;transition:all .18s;position:relative;overflow:hidden}
.ac::after{content:'';position:absolute;bottom:0;left:0;right:0;height:1px;background:linear-gradient(90deg,transparent,var(--cyan),transparent);opacity:0;transition:opacity .2s}
.ac:hover{border-color:var(--b3);transform:translateY(-2px)}.ac:hover::after{opacity:1}
.ac-num{font-family:'Bebas Neue',sans-serif;font-size:2.2rem;color:var(--b2);line-height:1;margin-bottom:6px}
.ac-title{font-weight:700;font-size:.95rem;margin-bottom:6px;color:var(--cyan)}
.ac-desc{font-size:.79rem;color:var(--dim);line-height:1.65;margin-bottom:9px}
.ac-how{font-size:.76rem;color:var(--dim);background:var(--s2);border-radius:6px;padding:10px 12px;border:1px solid var(--b1);line-height:1.65}
.ac-how strong{color:var(--amb)}
code{font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:.75rem;background:var(--b1);padding:1px 5px;border-radius:3px;color:var(--cyan)}

/* HEALTH */
.hg{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fill,minmax(290px,1fr));gap:13px}
.hc{background:var(--card);border:1px solid var(--b1);border-radius:11px;padding:17px}
.hc-top{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:11px;margin-bottom:11px}
.hc-em{font-size:22px}
.hc-title{font-weight:700;font-size:.9rem}
.hc-sub{font-size:.73rem;color:var(--dim)}
.hc-body{font-size:.79rem;color:var(--dim);line-height:1.7}
.hc-body strong{color:var(--txt)}
.hc-tags{display:flex;gap:5px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-top:9px}

@media(max-width:700px){
  .logo{font-size:2rem}
  .grid,.grid2,.ag,.hg{grid-template-columns:1fr}
  .sg{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr)}
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="bg-orbs"><div class="orb orb1"></div><div class="orb orb2"></div><div class="orb orb3"></div></div>
<div class="bg-grid"></div>

<div class="wrap">

<header>
  <div>
    <div class="logo">IMPERIO LIBRE</div>
    <div class="tagline">100% gratuito · Arch Linux · Alexis Granados · Full Stack + Coach + Automatizaciones</div>
  </div>
  <div class="hpills">
    <div class="hp c">50+ procesos</div>
    <div class="hp g">$0 / mes</div>
    <div class="hp a">Arch ✓</div>
  </div>
</header>

<div class="tabs">
  <div class="tab active" onclick="show('semanas',this)">📅 Planner Semanal</div>
  <div class="tab" onclick="show('redes',this)">📱 Redes & Mensajes</div>
  <div class="tab" onclick="show('productividad',this)">⚡ Productividad</div>
  <div class="tab" onclick="show('ia',this)">🤖 Asistentes IA</div>
  <div class="tab" onclick="show('salud',this)">🧠 Salud Mental</div>
  <div class="tab" onclick="show('tech',this)">💻 Tech & Arch</div>
  <div class="tab" onclick="show('roadmap',this)">🚀 Roadmap</div>
  <div class="tab" onclick="show('stack',this)">⚙️ Stack Ideal</div>
</div>

<!-- ════ PLANNER SEMANAL ════ -->
<div class="sec active" id="semanas">
  <div class="intro">
    Haz clic en cualquier día para ver <strong>exactamente qué hacer, en qué orden y con qué herramienta</strong>. Diseñado para TDAH: tareas cortas, claras, nada ambiguo. Cada semana cubre tus 6 áreas activas: Vyper Team, Web, TikTok, n8n, Ciberseguridad y Salud Mental.
  </div>
  <div class="week-grid" id="weekGrid"></div>
  <div id="dayDetail"></div>

  <div style="margin-top:36px;padding-top:24px;border-top:1px solid var(--b1)">
    <div class="cat-head">
      <div class="cat-icon" style="background:var(--pur2)">🗂️</div>
      <div class="cat-title" style="color:var(--pur)">Tus 6 Áreas de Vida Activas</div>
    </div>
    <div class="grid">
      <div class="card cp"><div class="card-top"><div class="card-em">⚽</div><div><div class="card-name">Vyper Team — 2 Rosters (16 jugadores)</div><div class="card-tool">Coaching · Psicología Deportiva</div></div></div><div class="card-desc">Gestión de 2 equipos amateur con meta de llevarlos a nivel semiprofesional. Bots de Telegram para cada roster, seguimiento de rendimiento, análisis táctico y psicología deportiva aplicada.</div><div class="card-tags"><span class="tc">Activo</span><span class="tp">Prioridad alta</span></div></div>
      <div class="card cc"><div class="card-top"><div class="card-em">🌐</div><div><div class="card-name">Portfolio Web — Completar y publicar</div><div class="card-tool">GitHub Pages · HTML/CSS/JS</div></div></div><div class="card-desc">Tu sitio tiene potencial enorme pero secciones incompletas. Documentar tus proyectos reales (bots, n8n, Vyper) lo convierte en tu CV vivo más poderoso.</div><div class="card-tags"><span class="tc">En progreso</span><span class="tf">GitHub free</span></div></div>
      <div class="card cr"><div class="card-top"><div class="card-em">🎬</div><div><div class="card-name">TikTok — Coaching & Psicología Deportiva</div><div class="card-tool">CapCut AI · Canva · Metricool</div></div></div><div class="card-desc">Volver a publicar con sistema de batching: graba 4 videos un día, publicas toda la semana sin tocar nada. CapCut AI hace la edición, Metricool programa todo automáticamente.</div><div class="card-tags"><span class="tai">Reactivar</span><span class="tf">Gratis</span></div></div>
      <div class="card ca"><div class="card-top"><div class="card-em">🤖</div><div><div class="card-name">n8n + Telegram — Centro de Automatización</div><div class="card-tool">n8n self-hosted · Telegram Bot API</div></div></div><div class="card-desc">Bots de Telegram que ya manejas más aprendizaje de n8n para flujos más complejos. En Arch Linux corre local, gratis, sin límites. Tu habilidad más valiosa a largo plazo.</div><div class="card-tags"><span class="ta">Aprendiendo</span><span class="tf">100% gratis</span><span class="tc">Arch ✓</span></div></div>
      <div class="card cg"><div class="card-top"><div class="card-em">🔐</div><div><div class="card-name">Ciberseguridad & Informática Forense</div><div class="card-tool">TryHackMe · Wireshark · Autopsy</div></div></div><div class="card-desc">TryHackMe tiene ruta gratuita desde cero. Wireshark, Autopsy y The Sleuth Kit corren perfecto en Arch. Nivel básico alcanzable en 3 meses con 30 min/día.</div><div class="card-tags"><span class="ta">Nuevo</span><span class="tf">Gratis</span><span class="tc">Arch ✓</span></div></div>
      <div class="card cb"><div class="card-top"><div class="card-em">🧠</div><div><div class="card-name">Salud Mental — TDAH + TLP</div><div class="card-tool">Rutinas · DBT · Focusmate</div></div></div><div class="card-desc">Rutinas específicas para TDAH y habilidades DBT para TLP. Sin esto el resto del sistema no funciona. Se integra en tu día sin apps extra — solo hábitos en TickTick y diario en Notion.</div><div class="card-tags"><span class="tp">Base de todo</span><span class="tf">Gratis</span></div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ════ REDES & MENSAJES ════ -->
<div class="sec" id="redes">
  <div class="intro">
    <strong>Una vez, en todos lados.</strong> Grabas un video de coaching → CapCut lo edita → Metricool lo publica en 5 redes → ManyChat responde comentarios automáticamente → n8n manda el resumen a tu Telegram. Sin tocar nada más. Todo gratis.
  </div>
  <div class="cat">
    <div class="cat-head"><div class="cat-icon" style="background:var(--red2)">🎬</div><div class="cat-title" style="color:var(--red)">Crear y Distribuir Contenido</div><div class="cat-badge">Todo unificado</div></div>
    <div class="grid">
